  "text": "[13] The source function, i.e. the spatio-temporal basal stress field, can be directly deduced from the landslide simulations. In order to strictly preserve the force balance between the initial and final states, third order terms in the thin layer asymptotic development have to be included in the calculation of the three-dimensional stress field T(x, t) by surface unit dx/c [CITATION_1] only used first order terms)",
